
<Lesson stage="2" page="5" type="Reading Check">
<APageParagraph activityIntroClip="uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3"  pencil="p3" skipIntro="true">
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>I like coming to visit Abigail.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>I am so glad to get away from the city with all its crowds and noise.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>      
      <sentence>
         <text>All those cars, buses and trucks make noise and smells.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>They can knock you down in the blink of an eye.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>You have to get out of the way as quick as you can.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		 <text>Out here it is full of trees and animals.</text>
		 <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	   </sentence>
	   <sentence>
		<text>But you have to watch out for the skunks, because they stink.</text>
		 <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	 </sentence>
   </paragraph>
   <paragraph>
      <sentence>
         <text>CR</text>
         <clip></clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>It is the most fun when we come to visit in July.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>We come every year for the picnic and fireworks.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
		  <text>Before the fireworks we have hot dogs, coleslaw, potato salad and root beer.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>First, I have to help my aunt frost the flag cake.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>Then we all wear red, white and blue.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>We watch the parade and then get ready for the fireworks.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
  </paragraph>
  <paragraph>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>CR</text>
		  <clip></clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
		  <text>I get to sit high up on the edge of the fire truck to watch.</text>
		  <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Those hoses are lumpy but I don't mind.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>Up here I can see it all.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
         <text>I have a great view to the shore.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
	  </sentence>
	  <sentence>
         <text>I can also lay back and see all the jewels in the sky.</text>
         <clip>uk/assets/sound/whiteSpace.mp3</clip>
      </sentence>
   </paragraph>
